  "intro": [
    "This is the academic corpus, kept the way The Quarry keeps the personal writing. It reads as the transcript reads, every course in the order it was taken, from the Rio Grande Valley to Austin. Beneath each course a slot is left open.",
    "The essays will be set into them one at a time, out of order as they are found, then put back into sequence here, so that as the slots fill the record becomes a chronological compilation of the academic writing. For now the frame is empty, and that is the point of it."
  ],
